recall: Senna and alvira decide to dine at a restauraunt to celebrate the growth of alvira's tomatoes. little does she know, senna has a big proposal planned. they had been going out for a while, and he wants to ask her to marry him. the restaurant is beautiful, and the food is delicious. when they are done with their meal, senna pulls out a ring and asks her the question. the restaurant watches as she accepts the proposal.

Emanualla and liam are in a grocery store preparing to get food for a dinner party. they initially start fighting about aribitrary things while picking out the food they will need, including pasta. eventually, they decide to break up because they realize they are not good for each other. they go to the checkout line, and pay the thirty dollars for the groceries. they decide to host the dinner party anyway, since they doon't want to tell people that they broke up just yet.

Isabel are returning home after meeting with isabel's parents. sven plans on proposing to isabel but forgets to hide the ring well. he leaves it in his pocket, and at security, the guard asks him to empty his pockets. having no other option, sven proposes to isabel right then and there, leading to her running away. she eventually says yes and texts her best friend with the great news.

Ms. bianchi and ms. morrison decide to meet at a grocery store to discuss a business deal. ms. bianchi wants ms. morrison to stock her gourmet cheeses in her stores, but ms. morrison is not very interested. after going back and forth, she finally agrees, and there is a deal made.

Anna runs into david at the airport with a trolly on accident. the incident leads them to start  talking and they get delayed at security. right before it is time for anna to board her plane, david asks her to dinner, which she accepts.

Charlie and alma are having lunch at a restaurant, but they do not know each other. eventualy, they get to talking, and charle asks alma out on a date that evening to a concert he is going to. she accepts, and they seem to hit it off.

James and teresaare at the airport about to miss their flights. teresa neglected to take her computer out of her bag, but good thing the security line already was delayed. they eventually make their flight.
